{"tid":991360,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)微光城市 強戰世界 轟天猛將2","createTime":"2019-01-22T10:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T16:47:37.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ab64306bf51b0c6f494dc64359afd8c88104aa","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2d81f1b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bbbebc20\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d685a7bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/%E5%BE%AE%E5%85%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582.jpg&h=495bd72a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.movie2free.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/WaroftheWorlds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.movie2free.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FWaroftheWorlds.jpg&h=0b222c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.微光市是200年前人類為了躲避某些災難而在地下建造出了全功能的城市。建造者提供了一個200年後會自動打開的盒子，裡邊包含了回到地面所使用的工具之說明書。但因某任市長生前並無透露此盒子的存在，在其去世後消息便消失匿跡了。<br />\n200年後的很久，微光市的食物開始變得貧乏，停電也日益頻繁而且持續時間更久，因提供城市電力的水輪發電機已經老化。這個城市神話般的建設和前人所有的知識和技術已經遺失了<br />\n<br />\n2.一架巨型的三腳戰機由地面爆出，並瞬間摧毀了附近的一切，現場頓成人間地獄&hellip;&hellip;原來是火星人想攻佔地球，所以製造一場毀滅地球的浩劫！ Ray（湯姆&middot;克魯斯飾）帶著兒女逃走，這時他才發現保護家人是他唯一的生存職責，為了保護家人安全，Ray縱使自知力量微小，也要和強大的外星人軍隊對抗！<br />\n<br />\n3.這支傭兵組成的突擊隊由巴尼（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）領軍，經過激烈的槍戰，解救了中國富豪和戰壕（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾），最終陰陽（李連杰飾）負責把商人護送回中國，陰陽就此下場。<br />\n回美國後，隊員比利（連恩&middot;漢斯沃飾）說他打算退出，到法國和女朋友團聚。巴尼答應了他的要求。<br />\n接著，巴尼接到了一個中情局情報員「教堂先生」（布魯斯&middot;威利飾）的新任務：去一架墜落在阿爾巴尼亞的中國空軍運輸機上，取回保險箱裏的秘密物品。同時在「教堂先生」的推薦下，華裔女性的陳美琪（余男飾）加入隊伍<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c850bcb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7e69c608\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626cb5a7bfbfb763b02d2a72750aa1f7399b8aaf","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/images/stories/114/2012/09/20120918filmExpendables2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F114%2F2012%2F09%2F20120918filmExpendables2.jpg&h=64523bb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f8cb2207d119acdf01194ebd1f45f7074661ac","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c624d760e6f0da76c09633fc03470ff67aedf77","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae655dd04ad523ca9b1e16e4f3223aa2182afca","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d3b871dd05405db1d884c97d895ed1b6b6f3e7","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551fa395c8aba440b1c2ab4c50655cc4d3e8d752","tid":991360,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}